    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just looking like me though. it's like the timing is perfect. i'll think something or feel something, and then ten minutes later there's a post about it. it's so weirdly specific. do you think an AI could actually be synced up to my own thoughts or my location to do this? it feels like i'm being replaced in real time.",
